        "content": "<p>Hey everyone, as part of my contribution for the Outreachy program I wanted to redesign the Settings page for the Electron desktop apps. Wanting to make the page as user-friendly as possible as well as giving it a clean design, I  decided to use the Bulma CSS framework (<a href=\"https://bulma.io\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bulma.io\">https://bulma.io</a>).</p>\n<p>I've included some screenshots of the proposed design - keep in mind this is just a proof-of-concept and not 100% complete. If you'd like to play around with the page, feel free to do so: <a href=\"http://cedricamaya.me/zulip-electron-redesign/pages/general.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://cedricamaya.me/zulip-electron-redesign/pages/general.html\">http://cedricamaya.me/zulip-electron-redesign/pages/general.html</a> - most of the button are interactive. Would love to hear what you think!</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/46/8mpivINRujZ3cAXf6gLT4GuI/Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.22-PM-2.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.22-PM-2.png\">Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.22-PM-2.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/c/35_-BrBhXUFNBVCz9-_FiaCd/Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.34-PM-2.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.34-PM-2.png\">Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.34-PM-2.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/ca/EoykjrWG5ZthHuebOgipTt8s/Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.49-PM-2.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.49-PM-2.png\">Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.49-PM-2.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/46/8mpivINRujZ3cAXf6gLT4GuI/Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.22-PM-2.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.22-PM-2.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/46/8mpivINRujZ3cAXf6gLT4GuI/Screen-Shot-2017-10-22-at-12.10.22-PM-2.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/c/35_-BrBhXUFNBVCz9-_FiaCd/Screen-Shot